Invocation Name: workout buddy
des:
Give it a time and a body part to workout and you are good to go! The skill can only handle short workout no longer than 10 minutes. Here are the features :
1. Gives an overview of today's workout
2. Randomize workout every time!
3. Customize you workout by telling Alexa which body part you want to work on:
 1.Core
 2. Leg
 3. Arm
 3. Glute
